data.description: Secluded well-cared-for home located in the desirable Westlake Valley. Long & beautiful drive, showcasing the lovely private, wooded setting that is ideal for quiet evenings with the family or for entertaining! This home has everything! Two master suites. Main master downstairs is massive, exposed brick, sitting area, separate shower & tub, double vanities & walk-in clst. Large kitchen w/loads of cabinets, coffee bar, pantry, & a breakfast area that opens up into the back patio & fenced-in yard. Formal dining, family room w/fireplace, & an office. Upstairs has 3 bedrooms, 2 of which have a bonus room attached. The basement has an additional family room, full bath, w/separate entrance & private patio w/fire pit. If that isn't enough the walk-up attic is huge, used as a bedroom & office, w/full bath. NO HOA. Join the Westlake Valley Club for access to the community pool, tennis & clubhouse. New flooring & paint.
